# Keep the image build fast + deterministic. Critically, exclude the host's Nx cache and node_modules
# so `COPY . .` cannot poison the in-container build with foreign cache entries (the Nx
# "unknown local cache" error) — npm ci installs node_modules fresh inside the image, and Nx builds
# with a clean cache.
.git
.gitignore
node_modules
**/node_modules
.nx
**/.nx
dist
**/dist
tmp
coverage
**/coverage
*.log
.aegis
.env.local
**/.env.local
docker-compose.e2e.yml
mono_crash*
.DS_Store
# NOTE: docs/ is intentionally NOT ignored — the gateway webpack build copies docs/api/openapi.yaml
# into the bundle for the live /api-docs Swagger UI.
